    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1 H3C LA2608 室内无线网关用户手册",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            92,
            60,
            613,
            85
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.1 概述",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            92,
            102,
            196,
            123
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "H3C LA2608-GM/GU 室内无线网关（以下简称 LA2608）可以为用户提供无线服务，为了实现对设备的管理，LA2608需要通过 3G/4G网络连接到运营商无线控制器。",
        "bbox": [
            139,
            138,
            905,
            175
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/df229fcb5e3b222c3e04ab69084b325f0e67f1de80f7d4e78b7826b543232f5d.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            144,
            188,
            186,
            213
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "说明",
        "bbox": [
            188,
            197,
            226,
            213
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "目前，LA2608只支持与 H3C公司的无线控制器互通。",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            224,
            564,
            241
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2 配置LA2608与无线控制器互通",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            282,
            484,
            302
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "如 图 1 所示，LA2608 安装了SIM卡，通过 3G/4G网络连接到运营商无线控制器，并向用户提供无线服务。关于LA2608的安装方法，请参见“H3C LA2608室内无线网关 快速安装指南”。",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            320,
            905,
            356
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "图1 配置 LA2608与无线控制器互通",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            362,
            431,
            378
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/4ccee3c380f5b5eebb16634b6395a8bb9bfc14476278ece11f5321e85f98b226.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            147,
            391,
            808,
            581
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2.1 配置LA2608",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            92,
            627,
            263,
            643
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1) 配置拨号访问组的拨号控制列表",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            659,
            440,
            675
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "algorithm",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_footnote": [],
        "code_body": "<LA2608>system-view  \n[LA2608]dialer-rule 1 ip permit  \n(2) 配置 DCC 拨号",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            682,
            418,
            733
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/957b37753e127740347a1fc8cca1d3cd84d54a55ed1d249fc14ae43def77c1c4.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            146,
            747,
            188,
            771
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "dialer number命令用来配置发起呼叫的拨号串，不同运营商的拨号串不同，请用户在配置前向网络运营商获取发起呼叫的拨号串。",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            781,
            905,
            817
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "algorithm",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_footnote": [],
        "code_body": "[LA2608]interface Cellular-Ethernet2/0   \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]ip address cellular-allocated   \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer enable-circular   \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer-group 1   \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer timer idle 0",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            850,
            647,
            931
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "page_number",
        "text": "1",
        "bbox": [
            504,
            948,
            517,
            959
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "algorithm",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_footnote": [],
        "code_body": "[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer timer autodial 5   \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer number \\*99# autodial   \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]nat outbound   \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]quit   \n(3) 配置 DNS 解析功能   \n[LA2608]dns resolve   \n(4) 配置静态路由   \n[LA2608]ip route-static 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 Cellular-Ethernet2/0   \n(5) 指定运营商无线控制器的 IP地址   \n[LA2608] wlan ac ip 60.191.99.143",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            51,
            665,
            237
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2.2 配置运营商无线控制器",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            92,
            248,
            352,
            267
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/8c3789bec91cf0b1bfc1305e07efb6be5d28185d9627bddda68d86ab6718de9b.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            146,
            289,
            188,
            313
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "说明",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            189,
            298,
            226,
            314
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "如下配置仅供参考，运营商可根据实际情况进行调整。",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            324,
            561,
            340
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1) 创建业务 VLAN (1) 创建业务 VLAN",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            142,
            374,
            314,
            390
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "algorithm",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_footnote": [],
        "code_body": "<AC>system-view  \n[AC]vlan 2  \n[AC-vlan2] quit  \n(2) 创建 WLAN-ESS 接口并加入业务 VLAN  \n[AC]interface WLAN-ESS 1  \n[AC-WLAN-ESS1]port access vlan 2  \n[AC-WLAN-ESS1]quit  \n(3) 配置明文方式的服务模板  \n[AC]wlan service-template 1 clear  \n[AC-wlan-st-1]ssid ssidh3c  \n[AC-wlan-st-1]bind WLAN-ESS 1  \n[AC-wlan-st-1]service-template enable  \nPlease wait... Done.  \n[AC-wlan-st-1]quit  \n(4) 开启自动 AP 功能  \n[AC]wlan auto-ap enable  \n[AC]wlan ap 2608 model LA2608 id 1  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]serial-id auto  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]radio 1  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]service-template 1  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]radio enable  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]quit  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]quit  \n(5) 配置 VLAN 接口 IP 地址  \n[AC]interface Vlan-interface 1  \n[AC-Vlan-interface1]ip address 60.191.99.143 255.255.0.0  \n[AC-Vlan-interface1]quit  \n[AC]interface Vlan-interface 2  \n[AC-Vlan-interface2]ip address 10.249.136.1 255.255.252.0  \n[AC-Vlan-interface2]quit  \n(6) 使能 DHCP 服务，配置 DHCP 地址池",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            382,
            640,
            941
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "page_number",
        "text": "2",
        "bbox": [
            504,
            948,
            517,
            959
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_footnote": [],
        "code_body": "```ini\n[AC]dhcp enable\n[AC]dhcp server ip-pool vlan2\n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]network 10.249.136.0 22\n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]gateway-list 10.249.136.1\n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]dns-list 218.201.96.130\n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]quit\n```",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            51,
            532,
            148
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2.3 验证LA2608 与无线控制器是否连通",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            92,
            162,
            468,
            179
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "在无线控制器上执行 display wlan ap 命令，state 字段显示为“R/M”，表示 LA2608 与无线控制器之间已经建立连接。",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            194,
            907,
            230
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "algorithm",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_footnote": [],
        "code_body": "<Sysname> display wlan ap all   \nTotal Number of APs configured : 1   \nTotal Number of configured APs connected : 1   \nTotal Number of auto APs connected : 0   \nAP Profiles   \nState : I = Idle, J = Join, JA = JoinAck, IL = ImageLoad   \nC = Config, R = Run, KU = KeyUpdate, KC = KeyCfm   \nM = Master, B = Backup   \nAP Name State Model Serial-ID   \nap1 R/M LA2608 036286A054000033",
        "bbox": [
